Winning numbers drawn in 'Rolling Cash 5' game
03 Nov 2019, 00:28 by The Associated Press
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening's drawing of the Ohio Lottery's "Rolling Cash 5" game were:
06-12-14-25-26
(six, twelve, fourteen, twenty-five, twenty-six)
Estimated jackpot: $353,000
